10 People were Killed and 8 injured after a taxi and bakkie collided in yet another Limpopo Crash.  The horrific accident happened in the Sekhukhune District at Dehoop dam just a few hours after three people were killed in another Limpopo crash near Kranskop on N1. 10 people died, 3 people sustained minor injuries, 2 patients was found in serious condition while another 3 sustained critical injuries.    The injured were transported to Jane Furse Hospital. Authorities are investigating the cause of the crash.